resources.string: While all of us have gone through the renting experience here in Jaipur at least for once, most of us are still least aware about the official laws governing it. It\'s better to be informed about what Indian government laws have to tell about renting practices so that you stay cautious against any fraud in future.

You can book a home in a well laid out and Semi-Furnished Semi-Furnished apartment in sirsi road, jaipur at a rent of Rs 20000. This apartment is located in a good locality with a good view and is great for a family with 3 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms. It has 1 parking space too. The area of the apartment is 2000 square feet and has 1 balcony. This apartment is facing towards the street and has a good view from the apartment.
